<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Wagyu Burger Details - Roomie Guest</title>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&amp;family=Playfair+Display:wght@600;700&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script>
        tailwind.config = {
            darkMode: "class",
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        "primary": "#1052d5",
                        "background-light": "#f8f9fb",
                        "royal-blue": "#0a3d91"
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        "sans": ["Plus Jakarta Sans", "sans-serif"],
                        "serif": ["Playfair Display", "serif"]
                    },
                    borderRadius: {
                        "DEFAULT": "1rem",
                        "lg": "1.5rem",
                        "xl": "2rem",
                        "2xl": "2.5rem",
                        "full": "9999px"
                    },
                },
            },
        }
    </script>
<style type="text/tailwindcss">
        @layer utilities {
            .no-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar {
                display: none;
            }
            .no-scrollbar {
                -ms-overflow-style: none;
                scrollbar-width: none;
            }
            .liquid-glass {
                @apply bg-white/30 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 shadow-lg;
            }
            .glass-morphism {
                @apply bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/40 shadow-lg;
            }
            .liquid-glow {
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.15) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 100%);
            }
        }
    </style>
<style>
        body {
            min-height: max(884px, 100dvh);
        }
    </style>
<style>
    body {
      min-height: max(884px, 100dvh);
    }
  </style>
  </head>
<body class="bg-background-light font-sans text-slate-900 antialiased">
<div class="relative flex min-h-screen w-full flex-col overflow-x-hidden mx-auto max-w-md bg-white shadow-2xl">
<div class="relative w-full h-[400px] overflow-hidden">
<div class="w-full h-full bg-center bg-cover scale-105" style='background-image: url("https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuB6fyb6EDDwPcPl_lBAAyNzOPJfA9e6X-_iu7VE2CbhT02gDJehfdTvnPb8Xoq3Wnpc3uIZgwMD8hh-qd92ZL4Y_o9F8CwEaB849IX4g9d77qJFv1yUKpvZcxjqvUwGb6OGwmbYJHAMtKT6SFwNF6Va7pa8OfrpbvGRSgWi_L9I0cIVu9vFdzfi1kXWK1Pw5bBTX_qi9oEUBJLyG44TxNftd4ozYZaygqZEu8-M37YEJRcz-ZaGQQR-xCml3ZCu-TzZhu0c0v68zIPi");'></div>
<div class="absolute top-12 left-6">
<button class="liquid-glass flex size-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full text-white">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[24px]">arrow_back_ios_new</span>
</button>
</div>
<div class="absolute top-12 right-6">
<button class="liquid-glass flex size-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full text-white">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[24px]">favorite</span>
</button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative -mt-10 flex-1 bg-white rounded-t-[2.5rem] px-8 pt-10 pb-44">
<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-amber-50 text-amber-600 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full border border-amber-100">Chef's Signature</span>
<div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2.5 py-1 bg-emerald-50 rounded-full border border-emerald-100">
<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full"></div>
<span class="text-[10px] text-emerald-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Added to Order</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h1 class="font-serif text-4xl text-slate-900 mb-4 leading-tight">Wagyu Burger</h1>
<p class="text-slate-500 text-base leading-relaxed mb-10">
                Double aged cheddar, caramelized onions, and house secret sauce on a toasted brioche bun. Prepared with the finest hand-selected Wagyu beef.
            </p>
<div class="mb-10">
<h3 class="text-slate-900 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Customization</h3>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
<button class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white text-slate-600 text-sm font-medium hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                        Extra Bacon
                    </button>
<button class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white text-slate-600 text-sm font-medium hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                        Gluten-Free Bun
                    </button>
<button class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white text-slate-600 text-sm font-medium hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                        No Onions
                    </button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-8 py-6 border-y border-slate-50">
<div class="flex flex-col">
<span class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Calories</span>
<span class="text-slate-900 font-bold">840 kcal</span>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col">
<span class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Prep Time</span>
<span class="text-slate-900 font-bold">15-20 min</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 mx-auto max-w-md pointer-events-none">
<div class="px-6 pb-6 pointer-events-auto">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-xl border border-slate-100 p-3 rounded-[2rem] shadow-2xl shadow-slate-200/50">
<div class="px-4">
<span class="block text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Total Price</span>
<div class="flex items-baseline gap-1">
<span class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-none">$28.00</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 h-14 bg-royal-blue rounded-full flex items-center justify-between p-1 shadow-lg shadow-blue-900/20 relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute inset-0 liquid-glow pointer-events-none"></div>
<button class="size-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white/90 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors z-10">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">remove</span>
</button>
<span class="text-white text-lg font-bold z-10">1</span>
<button class="size-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white/90 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors z-10">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">add</span>
</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="px-6 pb-8 pointer-events-auto">
<div class="glass-morphism rounded-full px-4 py-2">
<div class="flex items-center justify-around h-12">
<a class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-slate-400" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[24px]">home</span>
<span class="text-[9px] font-bold uppercase tracking-tight">Home</span>
</a>
<a class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-primary" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[24px] fill-current" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">room_service</span>
<span class="text-[9px] font-bold uppercase tracking-tight">Services</span>
</a>
<a class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-slate-400" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[24px]">receipt_long</span>
<span class="text-[9px] font-bold uppercase tracking-tight">Orders</span>
</a>
<a class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-slate-400" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[24px]">person</span>
<span class="text-[9px] font-bold uppercase tracking-tight">Account</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

</body></html>